org.opengis.cite.iso19136

Class GML32

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengis.cite.iso19136.GML32

  • public class GML32
extends Object
    Contains various constants pertaining to the standard GML 3.2 content model as specified in ISO 19136:2007.
